CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "Charming Visitors...at the Frogs' swank formal ball at the Penn-Sheraton Hotel included the above group. Left to right: Mrs. Walter Williams, Philadelphia; Arthur Catlin, Cleveland; Walter Williams, Mrs. Walter Catlin, Cleveland; Mrs. Helen Matthews Ball, Los Angeles; Walter Gordon, Mrs. Arthur Catlin, Cleveland, Cleveland, and Mrs. Hugo Hyde, Philadelphia."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mrs. Walter Williams, Arthur Catlin, Walter Williams, Mrs. Walter Catlin, Helen Matthews Ball, Walter Gordon, Mrs. Arthur Catlin, and Mrs. Hugo Hyde, posed in Pittsburgh Room, Penn-Sheraton Hotel, for FROGS formal
